{
  "stem": "14060.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We had a very large household, foodwise and otherwise.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And you took a few pieces of cake.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You went-- as a child, you took it to the door.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The person took it off and put on for you their cakes and you brought it home.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "However, to the poorer people, I remember there were big, like the American shopping bags, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These big, brown paper bags, five kilo of beans and flour and eggs and butter.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And each family got a massive amount of that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, that was a gentlemanly way to give a present when it was appropriate.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they were obviously assisted by the community.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think this point I didn't bring out when I referred to the autonomous Jewish community, its power and its infrastructure of having been built up in a relatively short time.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm talking of basically 60 to 80 years, when the time of emancipation 'til the time of deportation.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And many of these shuls were built within 20, 30 years after the emancipation, at the-- at the turn of the century or thereabouts, before the First World War.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was due to the fact that the autonomous Orthodox or Neolog communities had the right of every family and members of the family to pay communal taxes.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These taxes were collectible by the community leadership in the same manner as income tax.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The amount which they had to pay was delegated to a finance committee by the-- the main committee of that community, or synagogue if you like to call it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't have [NON-ENGLISH] and so on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was just the two communities, finished.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, whilst it was collectible legally through the courts, I think I didn't even hear if there ever came to it.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
